values: credit for graphics in this post : If I add you, you HAVE to add me! Some things I look for .. * Tell me where you found me. * Don't add me til I say you're added. * Make sure we have somethings in common. * No drama!! * No fakers & no TyPIng Lyk dis ma'! * Update your journal .. I wanna read about you too - but I CANNOT stand those little surveys, quizzes, etc. every other post. * Comment! I'm not expecting a comment every entry but let me know you're reading! * Don't advertise stuff in my journal please! Maybe a suggestive link, but no banners or anything saying 'join this community!!' * If you don't hear from me after a week, get the hint!! If you've been cut, you've been banned. Don't take anything personal about it. I hate seeing the FRIENDS OF list. And when I ban the person, then i don't have to see the extra people. I ban everybody I cut, til they remove me from their list (I do check - and un-ban the person once ive been taken off). Sorry if you find this offensive or whatever, but I'm sorry.
Did a small friends cut.
CREDITS:

gatagurlie = <lj user="undermyskin">
<lj user="undermyskin"> = gatagurlie!

<center>I'm tired of the clutter IRL .. I'm tired of the clutter in my LJ ...
I want somewhat of a fresh start so: New name ... HUGE friends cut.
If I cut you, please do the same.

For those who I cut: I'll see you around LJ. I'm just cutting it down to the people that I want to stay close with. This is in no attempt to go back & forth & back again. I'm seriously just exhausted. I don't want to lose the people who I consider close friends. I had my battles and am just way too weak. My journal is about me. And this is me .. I truly apologize to those for being completely ignorant, I have no explanations and just wish you will forgive me. I'm being genuine. I'm not playing games. Like I said this is me. I love you guys. </center>
